  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/28/japan-attack-warning-system/\"><img alt=\"Japanese person checking a cellphone while on a bike\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/c82bd57f7e3939c92453291243a8c770/japanese-cellphone-user-ignat-gorazd-flickr.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 339px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n大家都知道日本的手机具备自然灾害警报功能，但考虑到其「邻居」朝鲜最近一直在蠢蠢欲动，日本总务省消防厅做出了为国内手机加入针对导弹袭击、恐怖活动等人为威胁的警报功能。据悉它将基于此前行之有效的灾害警报技术，在软件升级方面应该不会有太大问题。从 4 月 1 日起该功能便会正式上线，希望它最终只是防患于未然吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/28/japan-attack-warning-system/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://jen.jiji.com/jc/i?g=eco&amp;k=2014032800481\" target=\"_blank\">Jiji Press</a></span>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2014/3/28/5556832/japan-sending-missile-launch-notifications-to-phones\" target=\"_blank\">The Verge</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.fdma.go.jp/neuter/topics/houdou/h26/2603/260328_1houdou/09_houdoushiryou.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">FDMA (PDF)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/28/japan-attack-warning-system/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20859033/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/28/japan-attack-warning-system/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
